# Website vs club ops

| Topic | Edit here (website) | Edit in Excelsior-Fencing-Club |
|-------|---------------------|--------------------------------|
| News, schedule, coaches (public) | Yes | No |
| Board minutes, invoices, VSC PDFs | No | Yes |
| Grants, bylaws, accident reports | No | Yes |
| WellnessLiving / membership backend | No | Yes (org docs) |

Coach **email addresses** for public `Coaches.md` should match how the club wants to be contacted; internal mailshots may use the same addresses.

If a task spans both (e.g. tournament announcement + board record), do **website news in this repo** and **internal notes in the club repo**.

Club repo agent rules: `.cursor/rules/` on `Excelsior-Fencing-Club` (coaches for VSC, VSC workflow, organization layout).
